title: Footage Of Cops Handcuffing Sean Kingston After Altercation With Migos Emerges
text:
Home > Music > Footage Of Cops Handcuffing Sean Kingston After Altercation With Migos Emerges Footage Of Cops Handcuffing Sean Kingston After Altercation With Migos Emerges 2 1 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 22, 2017 at 09:59am Migos allegedly stomped out Sean Kingston in Vegas Tuesday night. 
An alleged altercation between Migos and Sean Kingston occurred Tuesday night in Las Vegas in which a member of Kingston's crew fired a single gunshot in the air, causing Migos to "pummel [Kingston] to the ground." 
By the time the cops arrived, both parties had fled. Authorities soon caught up with Kingston at a traffic stop. Cameraphone footage depicts him handcuffed and talking to police. According to TMZ , he was "semi-cooperative" during the questioning and not arrested.
